To build a meld program for simulator:
   -Make sure the src-bobby build environment is installed 
   	 cd into src-bobby
	 make build
	 make install 

   - cd into build/apps/sample-meld	 
   -define BBASE
      export BBASE=build/src-bobby
   -define MELDRAW
      export MELDRAW=redMove.meld
   -run make

   -to run simulator:
       executable is in  arch-*/ folder
       launch with -R 1 (launching with configurations untested)

   -To remake, first run make wipeout

untested


	 